        <div xml:id="AN5-kilavi"></div>
        <div xml:id="AN5">
            <lg type="edition"><l>aḷinilai <choice><seg>peṟāa</seg><seg>poṟāa</seg></choice> tamariya mukattaḷ</l>
<l>viḷinilai kēḷā ṭamiyaṇ meṉme</l>
<l>ṉalamiku cēvaṭi nilamvaṭuk koḷāak</l>
<l>kuṟuka <choice><seg>vantutaṉ</seg><seg>vantu</seg></choice> kūreyiṟu tōṉṟa</l>
<l>vaṟitakat teḻunta vāyaṉ muṟuvalaḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṇiya tuṇarā vaḷavai yoṇṇutal</l>
<l>viṉaitalaip paṭutal cellā niṉaivuṭaṉ</l>
<l>muḷinta vōmai <choice><seg>mutaiya</seg><seg>mutaiyalaṅ</seg></choice> <choice><seg>laṅkāṭṭup</seg><seg>kāṭṭup</seg></choice></l>
<l>paḷiṅkat taṉṉa palkāy nelli</l>
<l>mōṭṭirum pāṟai yīṭṭuvaṭ ṭēyppa</l>
<l>vutirvaṉa <choice><seg>paṭūuṅ</seg><seg>paṭūum</seg></choice> <choice><seg>katirteṟu</seg><seg>katirteṟuṅ</seg></choice> kavāaṉ</l>
<l>māytta pōla maḻukunuṉai tōṟṟip</l>
<l>pātti yaṉṉa kuṭumik kūrṅkal</l>
<l>viraṉuti citaikku nirainilai yatara</l>
<l>paraṉmuram pākiya payamil kāṉa</l>
<l>miṟappa veṇṇuti rāyi ṉaṟattā</l>
<l><choice><seg>ṟaṉṟeṉa</seg><seg>raṉṟeṉa</seg></choice> moḻinta toṉṟupaṭu kiḷavi</l>
<l>yaṉṉa vāka veṉṉunaḷ pōla</l>
<l>muṉṉaṅ kāṭṭi mukatti ṉuraiyā</l>
<l>vōvac ceytiyi ṉoṉṟuniṉain <choice><seg>toṟṟip</seg><seg>tēṟṟip</seg></choice></l>
<l>pāvai māytta <choice><seg>paṉinīr</seg><seg>paṇinīr</seg></choice> nōkkamō</l>
<l><choice><seg>ṭākat</seg><seg>ṭotta</seg></choice> toṭukkiya putalvaṉ puṉṟalait</l>
<l><choice><seg>tūnīr</seg><seg>tūyanīr</seg></choice> payanta tuṇaiyamai piṇaiyaṉ</l>
<l>mōyiṉa ḷuyirtta kālai māmalar</l>
<l>maṇiyuru viḻanta <choice><seg>vaṇiyiḻait</seg><seg>vaṇiyaḻi</seg></choice> tōṟṟaṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṭē <choice><seg>kaṭintaṉañ</seg><seg>kaṭintaṉeñ</seg></choice> celavē <choice><seg>yoṇṭoṭi</seg><seg>yoṇṭoṭī</seg></choice></l>
<l>yuḻaiya mākavu <choice><seg>miṉaivōḷ</seg><seg>miṉaiyōḷ</seg></choice></l>
<l>piḻaiyalaṇ mātō piritunā meṉiṉē.</l></lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>“While thinking, without going [further] to advance the work,</l>
<l rend="indent">	of the bright forehead, so much that [you] don’t perceive what [you] see,</l>
<l rend="indent">	of her with a dazzling smile, risen from [your] poor mind,</l>
<l rend="indent">	so that her sharp teeth appear, coming close</l>
<l rend="indent">	without [her] beautiful red feet getting hurt on the ground,</l>
<l rend="indent">	very softly, she alone who does not hear a sound,<note place="foot">I for one fail to make sense of nilai in both line 1 and 2, and I suspect that it has entered here simply to create a etukai.</note></l>
<l rend="indent">	she with a face <choice><seg>contrariated at not obtaining [your] care,</seg><seg>contrariated, [your] care not supporting [her],</seg></choice> </l>
<l>if you reckon to traverse</l>
<l>the barren forest that is [all] pebbles [and] gravel,</l>
<l rend="indent">	with roads hemmed in by toe-tip-ruining rows</l>
<l rend="indent">	of sharp stones with crests as if divided,</l>
<l rend="indent">	showing blunt tips as if they had been sharpened,</l>
<l>[and] slopes scorched by [sun] rays, where what has dropped</l>
<l rend="indent">	from the gooseberry tree with many crystal-like unripe fruits</l>
<l>occurs to resemble amassed pawns on the large rocks of the height,</l>
<l>in the pretty wilderness of ancient groves of dried Ōmai,</l>
<l rend="indent4">				it is not <choice><seg>the path of </seg><seg>for those who are </seg></choice> <choice><seg>virtue!”,</seg><seg>virtuous!”,</seg></choice> </l>
<l><choice><seg></seg><seg>– </seg></choice> while the words spoken of old</l>
<l>are thus, as if she were speaking,</l>
<l>showing what was before with [her] face, without talking,</l>
<l><choice><seg>by creating an image, thinking </seg><seg>thinking one thing, bringing </seg></choice> <choice><seg>one thing, persistently,</seg><seg>[it] up by creating an image,</seg></choice> </l>
<l>with [her] glance [filled] with <choice><seg>dewy </seg><seg>humble </seg></choice> water that makes [her] pupils disappear,</l>
<l>– seeing</l>
<l>the <choice><seg>appearance of [her with] adorning jewels who </seg><seg>appearance, adornments ruined, that </seg></choice> has lost <choice><seg>[her] </seg><seg>[its] </seg></choice> sapphire colour</l>
<l>of a dark blossom, at the time when she sighs, sniffing</l>
<l>the garland, fit for a mate, yielded by the fresh waters,</l>
<l>on the ruddy head of [her] son, restraining <choice><seg>[her feelings] in [her] bosom,</seg><seg>[herself] befittingly,</seg></choice> </l>
<l rend="indent">	we have chased away [the thought of] <choice><seg>going. Even though</seg><seg>going, [you with] bright bangles.</seg></choice> </l>
<l><choice><seg>we are near [her with] bright bangles she is desperate.</seg><seg>Even though we are near, she is like this.</seg></choice> </l>
<l>Won’t she break if we say that we’ll leave?</l></lg>
        </div>
